name: Set of 4 favourite finger puppets and song cards
description: 4 classic finger puppets and song cards. Five little ladybugs, Five dragonflies, Five Bees and Five little butterflies  Enjoy your time with your children by singing along to four favourite songs,  each finger puppet comes with their own  song card.  Children will not only love the fun and bright puppets, but they will be developing skills such recognising colours and  counting also  developing  cognitive, language, fine motor and turn taking skills.  Great for home or a  teaching resource for  childcare or school.

name: Old Macdonald finger puppets
description: Enjoy time with your children by  singing  along to the good old classic favourite,  "Old Macdonald had a farm".  Animals puppets include horse, pig, sheep, rooster and cow. Children will have fun whilst development skills such as cognitive, language, communication, listening, fine motor development and turn taking.
